fix(orders): prevent stock race conditions and refactor order persistence

- wrap order placement flow in database transaction
- apply lockForUpdate() when loading products (SELECT ... FOR UPDATE)
- ensure stock consistency under concurrent requests
- prevent overselling for low-stock products

- refactor order persistence:
  - rename createOrder() to persistOrder()
  - move transaction boundary to service handler
  - remove nested transaction for cleaner separation

- fix incorrect OrderPricingCalculatorService class reference

- add relationships:
  - User::store() via hasOneThrough
  - VendorProfile::store() via hasOne

